title: Extra EU27 Trade of Mineral Fuels Lubricants - Imports in 1000 Million ECU/EURO, World, 1999 - 2007
name: Extra EU27 Trade of Mineral Fuels Lubricants - Imports in 1000 Million ECU/EURO, World, 1999 - 2007
description:
The table shows the 10 main partners of the EU27 for that product group (according to the sum imports+exports). Imports are expressed in value terms and measured cif (cost, insurance, freight). Exports are expressed in value terms and measured fob (free on board). Balance = export - import.

Please note that the value -1 was used as a placeholder when no data was available.
